The Missing Elves Conversation Log at the Inn

[pagebreak] I've heard rumors about a certain pirate crew targeting young female elves orphaned during the war... That part is nothing unusual... But from what I've heard, while they humiliate and frighten the elves, they don't forcefully injure them or make them bleed. The environment isn't exactly ideal, but their goal seems to be educating them and raising them to become fully capable individuals... Some of the raised elves even married nobles, while others became soldiers. You could call it an orphanage at sea. But this didn't last long.
